  "texts": [
    "To find a match in the generated report, we use an advanced version of Gestalt pattern matching (Ratcliff and Obershelp, 1988) available in the Python library difflib.",
    "We use the default cutoff threshold of 0.6.",
    "This value strikes a balance between matching every word as a target and matching only exact overlaps.",
    "The latter is undesirable because it ignores different grammatical forms of a word.",
    "As a result, some unrelated words will inevitably be matched."
  ],
